<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>209</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Kan dawt Bawi i khuaruahhar vel cu, Kan sual palhnak nakin a ngan
 deuh, Kal-va-ry tlang ah khin a chuak cang, Khika ah tuufa thi cu a luang.

[C1]
   Pathian (Pathian dawtnak) dawtnak (Pathian dawtnak) ngaihthiam le
   thianter khotu dawtnak, Pathian (Pathian dawtnak) dawtnak (Pathian
   dawtnak) Sualnak vialte a teitu dawtnak.

[V2]
 Sualnak le hnabei donghnak nih cun, Tilet bangin kan khuh deng
 hmanhseh, Khi nakin a ngan deuhmi vel nih, Himnak vailam ah cun a kan
 hruai.

[C2]
   Pathian (Pathian dawtnak) dawtnak (Pathian dawtnak) ngaihthiam le
   thianter khotu dawtnak, Pathian (Pathian dawtnak) dawtnak (Pathian
   dawtnak) Sualnak vialte a teitu dawtnak.

[V3]
 Sualnak hma-neh cu kan thup kho lo, Zei nih dah a thianh a tlengh
 khawh lai? Zoh tuah, khika ah thisen a luang, Hawhra nakin na rang deuh
 cang lai.

[C3]
   Pathian (Pathian dawtnak) dawtnak (Pathian dawtnak) ngaihthiam le
   thianter khotu dawtnak, Pathian (Pathian dawtnak) dawtnak (Pathian
   dawtnak) Sualnak vialte a teitu dawtnak.

[V4]
 Khuaruahhar dong lo sung bik vel cu, A zummi nih man loin an hmuh;
 Nannih Amah hmai hmuh a duhmi, Atu a vel kha i lak tuah u.

[C4]
   Pathian (Pathian dawtnak) dawtnak (Pathian dawtnak) ngaihthiam le
   thianter khotu dawtnak, Pathian (Pathian dawtnak) dawtnak (Pathian
   dawtnak) Sualnak vialte a teitu dawtnak.</lyrics>
<key>G</key>
<title>KAN SUAL NAKIN NGAN DEUHMI VEL CH209</title>
</song>